title: Did you win $70 million Powerball jackpot?: Oregon Lottery results
text:
The Oregon Lottery released results Wednesday night for several games, including the $70 million Powerball drawing.
Did you win?
Is your life fundamentally altered?
Here are the numbers.
Powerball : 15-20-29-31-40-1 x 2
Megabucks : 31-35-40-41-42-48 ($5.4 million jackpot)
Win for Life: 19-22-37-63
